        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "This gemstone grants its wearer a +2 item bonus to saving throws.  \n  \nEach *heartstone* is powered by the spirit of a specific night hag. If it\u2019s separated from her for 24 hours (or she\u2019s been dead for 24 hours), it becomes a nonmagical gemstone. A *heartstone* allows the hag to use additional occult innate spells: *ethereal jaunt* (9th level) and *bind soul* at will, and *shadow blast* twice per day.",
        "level": 9,
        "traits": [
            {
                "name": "Abjuration",
                "type": "trait",
                "edition": "legacy",
                "sources": [
                    {
                        "type": "source",
                        "name": "Core Rulebook",
                        "link": {
